videos.description: Iowa's Tyler Cook crushes a dunk on a nice pass from Luka Garza.

videos.headline: Cook hangs on rim after slam

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Vic Law hits a deep three-pointer for Northwestern, his 5th of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Law sinks 5th shot from deep in first half) 2019/02/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Law sinks 5th shot from deep in first half

videos.description: Dererk Pardon makes a nice low pass to Anthony Gaines who drives to the basket for a dunk.
videos.headline: Gaines crushes big dunk

videos.description: Dererk Pardon fakes a handoff and drives to the basket for the jam.

videos.description: Down 12 in the final 3 minutes, Iowa comes back to defeat Northwestern 80-79, led by Jordan Bohannon who hits the game-winning three.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Iowa has incredible comeback over Northwestern) 2019/02/10 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Iowa has incredible comeback over Northwestern
